spells.description:
Equip: Gain scendance every 8 seconds spent in combat.

scendance grants 145 of a random secondary stat for 15 sec, stacking up to 10 times.

Equip: Your abilities have a chance to stir the sac, releasing an egg which grants you 961 Agility. Each egg hatches after 1 min, and the new brood attacks your next target, inflicting 73,994 Nature damage over 8 sec.
